{"tid":2424893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[逃犯天堂]美國司法部起訴一名居港商人　涉嫌偷取通用電器技術","createTime":"2021-02-27T03:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T04:00:45.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8cdfaaf1f81633ce45eec9e42bcbc0c50bc7979","tid":2424893,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">不過係支那逃犯</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577814-20210227.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577814-20210227.htm&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=6bf03ec3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577814-20210227.htm&h=baf6b71c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577814-20210227.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國司法部起訴一名在香港居住的中國商人，指控他在2017年至2018年間，意圖偷取通用電器的半導體技術及商業機密。<br />\n<br />\n司法部表示，這名譯音姓吳的64歲商人，以及多名共謀人士，計劃偷取通用電器具有價值及敏感的「碳化矽金氧半場效晶體管」技術，並在中國進行生產及圖利。<br />\n<br />\n司法部表示，當局暫時未有拘捕這名商人，若果被告罪名成立，將面臨最高10年監禁及罰款25萬美元。"},{"pid":"baf6ea5f1a7033a67f8be32c2ceb49c89f41ce48","tid":2424893,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"Keyboard man <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eacae89d68dacd7c428459153a7a9d775bdbac4","tid":2424893,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"baf6ea5f1a7033a67f8be32c2ceb49c89f41ce48","tid":2424893,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"Keyboard man <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixYsiB3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FixYsiB3.png&h=fa99678c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n★支那好治癒gif貼圖區！（10）<